bilingual.source: He spends a lot of time fishing.

bilingual.target: 约翰的爸爸有一根钓鱼竿。

bilingual.source: Ali and Tim were fishing by the lake.
bilingual.target: 阿里和蒂姆在湖边钓鱼。

bilingual.source: In autumn, he goes fishing under the tree.
We always go fishing in the lake in summer.
bilingual.target: 我们夏天总是在湖里钓鱼。

bilingual.source: Does your father spend a lot of time fishing?
bilingual.target: 你爸爸花很多时间钓鱼吗？

bilingual.source: He asks whether we will go fishing on Sunday.
bilingual.target: 他问我们周日是否会去钓鱼。

yingyinNormal.en: I know what ice fishing is.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我知道冰上钓鱼是什么啦。

yingyinNormal.en: I love going fishing. Me too. And what do you need for a fishing trip? Fishing rods? No, the picnic basket.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我喜欢去钓鱼。我也是。去钓鱼度假你需要什么东西呢？鱼竿？不，野餐篮。

yingyinNormal.en: I remember, when I was a kid, me and my father, we went ice fishing out on Lake Wissota. Ice fishing is, you know, where you...
yingyinNormal.zh: 我小时候跟父亲到威苏塔湖，在冰上钓鱼，冰上钓鱼就是…

yingyinNormal.en: What we need is a fishing rod. Then we can catch the keys on a hook. Maybe Miss Rabb it sells fishing rods.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们需要是一根钓鱼竿。这样我们就能用鱼钩勾住钥匙。也许兔小姐那里有钓鱼竿卖。

yingyinNormal.en: What we need is a fishing rod. Then we can catch the keys on a hook. Maybe Miss Rabb it sells fishing rods.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们需要是一根钓鱼竿。这样我们就能用鱼钩勾住钥匙。也许兔小姐那里有钓鱼竿卖。

yingyinNormal.en: On the Hudson River. Isn't it a little early in the year to go fishing? Seeking the facts is hardly "fishing," Mr. Skiles.
yingyinNormal.zh: 是浮在哈德逊河上，今年这个时候去“钓鱼”是不是早了点？寻求事实跟“钓鱼”完全是两码事，斯基尔斯先生。

yingyinNormal.en: Do you sell fishing rods? We do, actually. I don't know why. You don't get fish in the mountains.
yingyinNormal.zh: 请问你们这里有钓鱼竿卖吗？我们有钓鱼竿，不知道为什么。你在山里根本吊不到鱼。

yingyinNormal.en: Do you sell fishing rods? We do, actually. I don't know why. You don't get fish in the mountains.
yingyinNormal.zh: 请问你们这里有钓鱼竿卖吗？我们有钓鱼竿，不知道为什么。你在山里根本吊不到鱼。

yingyinNormal.en: We are not fishing for fish. We are fishing for keys. My Daddy dropped the car keys down the drain.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们不要钓鱼，我们要钓车钥匙。我们的爸爸把车钥匙掉进排水道里了。

yingyinNormal.en: We are not fishing for fish. We are fishing for keys. My Daddy dropped the car keys down the drain.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们不要钓鱼，我们要钓车钥匙。我们的爸爸把车钥匙掉进排水道里了。

yingyinNormal.en: Then, we attach this fishing line to a small rope, and we pass that between the towers.
yingyinNormal.zh: 再把钓鱼线绑在一条绳子上，在两座塔楼之间传送。

yingyinNormal.en: Except for the summer and then we'd shelter with various hunting, shooting and fishing relations.
yingyinNormal.zh: 除了夏天的时候，我们会暂住亲戚家，一起狩猎钓鱼什么的。

yingyinNormal.en: I attach some fishing line to one of my juggling balls, and I throw it across to the other side where Jean-Louis is waiting.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我在杂耍球上绑了钓鱼线，丢到对面给尚路易。

yingyinNormal.en: No, no, no. I went to Greenland and then I got on a fishing vessel tracking Sean and ended up here in Iceland.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不，不，我去格陵兰，然后我登上了船钓鱼，跟踪肖恩跑到冰岛。

yingyinNormal.en: Now, the first time I played it white hat. My family was here. We went fishing, did the gold hunt in the mountains.
yingyinNormal.zh: 第一次来的时候，我全程演个好人，我家人也一起来了，我们一起去钓鱼，去山里淘金。

yingyinNormal.en: You know, maybe we didn't have opportunities like this when we were growing up, but right now, there's a dad that wants to take you on a fishing trip.
yingyinNormal.zh: 也许我们在长大的过程中没有这样的机会，但现在有位父亲真的要带你去钓鱼了。

yingyinNormal.en: It is Granddad Dog, Grandpa Pig and Gramppy Rabbit. Hello. Can Captain Dog come out to play? What? We're going on a fishing trip. On a boat. On the sea.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这是狗爷爷，猪奶奶和兔爷爷。你们好！狗船长能出来玩吗？什么？我们要去钓鱼旅行。坐船去。去海里。

yingyinNormal.en: Believe. Your Honor. This is a fishing expedition.
yingyinNormal.zh: 相信，法官阁下，这是非法调查。

yingyinNormal.en: Yeah, but it's actually pretty specific for a fishing expedition.
yingyinNormal.zh: 是，但这确实是对象非常明确的非法调查。

yingyinNormal.en: Spotted, Jenny Humphrey wading in the met fountain, fishing for change.
yingyinNormal.zh: 最新消息，珍妮跋涉于大都市博物馆喷泉之前，寻求改变...

数据源自2016.6-2023.6年8年间全四级试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight>考纲释义</highlight>
精选实考、考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>考频分布</highlight>

examination_example.sentence_trans: 政府官员提议在未来十年颁布禁渔令，以保护该地区濒临灭绝的野生鱼类。
